'''薩普托公司'''（Saputo Inc.，{{Tsx|SAP}}）是一家位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[蒙特利爾|蒙特利爾]]的[[乳製品|乳製品]]製造公司。是1954年由[[意大利裔加拿大人|意大利裔加拿大人]]朱塞佩·薩普托（Giuseppe Saputo）創立的奶酪商店發展而來的。現其產品包括奶酪、烘焙飾品和乳製品，是世界第12大乳製品製造公司。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.saputo.com/futures-candidates/default.aspx?id=38&langtype=4105 |title=Home - Candidates |publisher=Saputo |date= |accessdate=2013-11-15}}</ref>

薩普托公司是加拿大最大的乳製品加工公司，此外在美國、威爾士、德國和阿根廷也有服務。<ref>[http://www4.agr.gc.ca/AAFC-AAC/display-afficher.do?id=1182522993907 Agriculture and Agri-Food Canada - The Canadian Dairy Industry at a Glance] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120815122023/http://www4.agr.gc.ca/AAFC-AAC/display-afficher.do?id=1182522993907 |date=2012-08-15 }}</ref>

== 歷史==
[[Image:WTMTL_T23_DSC_5756.JPG|left]]
2001年薩普托公司以4.07億加元的價格購下[[Dairyworld_Foods|Dairyworld Foods]]公司。<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/business/story/2000/12/18/saputo001218.html | work=CBC News | title=Saputo Inc. spends $407 million for Dairyworld Foods | date=December 18, 2000}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.saputo.com/investors-and-medias/press-releases/detail.aspx?id=2349&langType=4105 |title=Inc. announces an agreement to acquire Dairyworld Foods - Investors and Media |publisher=Saputo |date= |accessdate=2013-11-15}}</ref>

2008年以4.65億加元的價格從[[喬治威斯頓公司|喬治威斯頓公司]]購下[[Neilson_Dairy|Neilson Dairy]]。<ref>{{cite web |last=Gazette |first=Montreal |url=http://www.canada.com/montrealgazette/news/business/story.html?id=d6799cff-a530-4748-a51a-75527e693f32 |title=Saputo acquires George Weston's Neilson dairy |publisher=Canada.com |date=2008-10-22 |accessdate=2013-11-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140308000907/http://www.canada.com/montrealgazette/news/business/story.html?id=d6799cff-a530-4748-a51a-75527e693f32 |archivedate=2014-03-08 }}</ref>

